        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>porcelain (material) [300010662], ceramic (material) [300235507], ceramic and ceramic by product [300151340], clay by product [300010462], clay [300010439], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
